issue.description:
The dashboard is only compatible with php 5.4 because of use of php syntaxes like declaring array with brackets :
$return->columns_title = [JText::_('COM_EASYSDI_DASHBOARD_SHOP_IND_TOPDOWNLOADS_COL1'),JText::_('COM_EASYSDI_DASHBOARD_SHOP_IND_TOPDOWNLOADS_COL2')];

or use of JSON_PRETTY_PRINT :
$json = json_encode($return, JSON_PRETTY_PRINT);

It should be compatible also with php 5.3.
